<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Zero Dash One &mdash; creative technology studio</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Zero Dash One is an independent creative technology studio in the Texas Hill Country. We design and build interactive web experiences, generative visual systems, and small-team product work.">
  <meta property="og:title" content="Zero Dash One">
  <meta property="og:description" content="Creative technology studio. Interactive web, generative visuals, small-team product builds.">
  <meta property="og:type" content="website">
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="Zero Dash One">
  <meta name="twitter:description" content="Creative technology studio. Interactive web, generative visuals, small-team product builds.">
  <meta name="version" content="1.0.0">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg">
  <script src="/qrcode.min.js"></script>
  <style>
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    html, body {
      width: 100%;
      background: #000;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      cursor: default;
      -webkit-user-select: text;
      user-select: text;
      font-family: 'SF Mono', Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }
    body {
      overflow-x: hidden;
      overflow-y: auto;
    }
    canvas {
      display: block;
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 1.5s ease-in;
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      z-index: 1;
    }
    canvas.loaded {
      opacity: 1;
    }
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
      width: 100%;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .info-panel {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 460px;
      max-width: 100%;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.88);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      padding: 56px 40px 80px;
      overflow-y: auto;
      z-index: 3;
      pointer-events: auto;
    }
    .info-panel header.brand {
      margin-bottom: 36px;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    }
    .info-panel header.brand h1 {
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .info-panel header.brand .tag {
      display: block;
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .info-panel .block { margin-bottom: 28px; }
    .info-panel .block:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .info-panel h2 {
      font-size: 10px;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .info-panel p {
      font-size: 13px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .info-panel p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .info-panel ul.svc {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .info-panel ul.svc li {
      padding: 12px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.55;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
    }
    .info-panel ul.svc li:first-child { border-top: none; padding-top: 4px; }
    .info-panel ul.svc strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .info-panel a {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
      transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
    }
    .info-panel a:hover { border-bottom-color: #fff; }
    .info-panel address {
      font-style: normal;
      font-size: 12px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .info-panel {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
        bottom: auto;
        min-height: 100vh;
        padding: 40px 24px 60px;
        border-right: none;
      }
      .hero { min-height: auto; }
    }

    main.copy {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 3;
      background: #000;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    }
    main.copy section {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 80px 24px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }
    main.copy section:last-of-type { border-bottom: none; }
    main.copy h2 {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    main.copy h3 {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.4;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    main.copy p, main.copy li {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    main.copy ul.services {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    main.copy ul.services li {
      padding: 18px 0;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr;
      gap: 24px;
      align-items: start;
    }
    main.copy ul.services li:last-child {
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    }
    main.copy ul.services .label {
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 0.18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
      padding-top: 3px;
    }
    main.copy ul.services .desc {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
    }
    main.copy a {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
      transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
    }
    main.copy a:hover { border-bottom-color: #fff; }
    .cta {
      margin-top: 32px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      main.copy section { padding: 56px 20px; }
      main.copy h3 { font-size: 18px; }
      main.copy ul.services li {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 6px;
      }
    }

    footer.contact {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 3;
      background: #000;
      text-align: center;
      font-family: 'SF Mono', Menlo, Consolas, monospace;
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
      padding: 32px 16px 28px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    }
    footer.contact a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: color 0.25s ease;
    }
    footer.contact a:hover {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
      text-decoration: underline;
    }
    footer.contact .sep {
      opacity: 0.5;
      margin: 0 6px;
    }
    footer.contact .honeypot {
      position: absolute;
      left: -9999px;
      top: -9999px;
      opacity: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      footer.contact { font-size: 9px; line-height: 1.7; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <noscript>
    <div style="position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:99;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:#000;color:#fff;font-family:Helvetica,sans-serif;text-align:center;">
      <div>
        <svg viewBox="0 0 64 64" width="64" height="64" style="margin-bottom:1rem;">
          <polygon points="32,8 56,56 8,56" fill="none" stroke="#fff" stroke-width="2"/>
        </svg>
        <h1 style="font-weight:300;letter-spacing:0.1em;">Zero Dash One</h1>
        <p style="opacity:0.5;margin-top:0.5rem;">Enable JavaScript to experience this site.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </noscript>

  <section class="hero">
    <aside class="info-panel" aria-label="About Zero Dash One">
      <header class="brand">
        <h1>Zero Dash One</h1>
        <span class="tag">Independent creative technology studio &middot; Bulverde, TX</span>
      </header>

      <div class="block">
        <h2>About</h2>
        <p>Zero Dash One LLC is an independent creative technology studio based in the Texas Hill Country. We design and build interactive web experiences, generative visual systems, and small-team product work for founders, agencies, and brands that care about craft.</p>
        <p>Engagements are remote, project-based, and led directly by the studio principal &mdash; no junior pass-through, no agency overhead.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="block">
        <h2>What we do</h2>
        <ul class="svc">
          <li><strong>Interactive Web</strong>Custom microsites, product launches, and one-off web pieces. The animation behind this panel is one of ours.</li>
          <li><strong>Generative Visuals</strong>Motion systems, generative identity assets, and simulation-based imagery for brands, products, and editorial use.</li>
          <li><strong>Site &amp; Product Builds</strong>Full-stack web builds for boutique brands and early-stage products. Design, code, deploy.</li>
          <li><strong>Creative Tech Consulting</strong>Discovery, prototyping, and technical direction for studios and agencies on a specific brief.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="block">
        <h2>How we work</h2>
        <p>Project-based with fixed scope and fixed price. Each engagement starts with a one-week paid discovery: scope, sketches, schedule, written proposal. We take on a small number of projects at a time.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="block">
        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          <a class="cx-mail" data-u="hello" data-d="zerodashone.com" href="#">hello at zerodashone dot com</a><br>
          <a class="cx-tel" data-t="8302835500" href="#">830 283 5500</a>
        </p>
        <address>
          Zero Dash One LLC<br>
          30131 Bulverde Ln. Unit #149<br>
          Bulverde, TX 78163
        </address>
      </div>

      <div class="block">
        <h2>Legal</h2>
        <p style="font-size:11px;">
          <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a> &middot; <a href="/terms">Terms of Service</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </aside>
  </section>

  <main class="copy">
    <section id="about">
      <h2>About</h2>
      <h3>Zero Dash One is an independent creative technology studio based in the Texas Hill Country.</h3>
      <p>We design and build interactive web experiences, generative visual systems, and small-team product work for founders, agencies, and brands that care about craft. Engagements are remote, project-based, and led directly by the studio principal &mdash; no junior pass-through, no agency overhead.</p>
      <p>The piece you scrolled past is a hand-written Canvas2D sketch shipped as a single, obfuscated, ~80 KB HTML file. It is also a demo of how we work: small, deliberate, and end-to-end.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="services">
      <h2>What we do</h2>
      <ul class="services">
        <li>
          <div class="label">Interactive Web</div>
          <div class="desc">Custom microsites, product launches, and one-off web pieces. Hand-rolled rendering, performance budgets, and a designed feel for everything that moves &mdash; not a template.</div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="label">Generative Visuals</div>
          <div class="desc">Motion systems, generative identity assets, and simulation-based imagery for brands, products, and editorial use. Output ranges from interactive web to high-resolution stills and short loops.</div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="label">Site &amp; Product Builds</div>
          <div class="desc">Full-stack web builds for boutique brands and early-stage products. Design, code, deploy. Modern stack &mdash; statically generated where it makes sense, edge-deployed, low-overhead to maintain.</div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="label">Creative Tech Consulting</div>
          <div class="desc">Discovery, prototyping, and technical direction for studios and agencies that need a creative-technology partner on a specific brief. Short engagements, written outputs, no retainer.</div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section id="how">
      <h2>How we work</h2>
      <p>Project-based with fixed scope and fixed price. Every engagement starts with a one-week paid discovery: scope, sketches, schedule, and a written proposal. From there, weekly check-ins through launch. No retainers, no monthly creep, no surprise invoices.</p>
      <p>We take on a small number of projects at a time and decline most inquiries. That&rsquo;s how the work stays good. If your timeline is right, we&rsquo;ll tell you. If it isn&rsquo;t, we&rsquo;ll tell you that too &mdash; and usually point you at someone better suited.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="contact">
      <h2>Get in touch</h2>
      <p>Have a project in mind? The fastest path is email.</p>
      <p class="cta">
        <a class="cx-mail" data-u="hello" data-d="zerodashone.com" href="#">hello at zerodashone dot com</a>
        <br>
        <a class="cx-tel" data-t="8302835500" href="#">830 283 5500</a>
        <br>
        30131 Bulverde Ln. Unit #149, Bulverde, TX 78163
      </p>
      <p>We respond to inbound inquiries within two business days.</p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="contact" role="contentinfo">
    <div>Zero Dash One LLC &mdash; creative technology studio &mdash; Bulverde, TX</div>
    <div>
      <a class="cx-mail" data-u="hello" data-d="zerodashone.com" href="#">hello at zerodashone dot com</a>
      <span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <a class="cx-tel" data-t="8302835500" href="#">830 283 5500</a>
    </div>
    <div>
      <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
      <span class="sep">&middot;</span>
      <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
    </div>
    <a class="honeypot" href="mailto:trap@zerodashone.invalid" tabindex="-1" aria-hidden="true">do not contact</a>
  </footer>
  <script>
    (function(){
      var at = String.fromCharCode(64);
      document.querySelectorAll('a.cx-mail').forEach(function(a){
        var addr = a.dataset.u + at + a.dataset.d;
        a.textContent = addr;
        a.setAttribute('href', 'mailto:' + addr);
      });
      document.querySelectorAll('a.cx-tel').forEach(function(a){
        var t = a.dataset.t;
        a.textContent = t.slice(0,3) + '.' + t.slice(3,6) + '.' + t.slice(6);
        a.setAttribute('href', 'tel:+1' + t);
      });
    })();
  </script>
  <script src="/sketch.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
